<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>文章约稿 · Arseeya</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c1f, #1a1a2e);
            color: #eee;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            background: #c5314b;
        }
        .commission-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #667eea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .coming-soon-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(233,69,96,0.2);
            border: 1px solid #e94560;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 0.3rem 1.2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .info-text {
            color: #ccc;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .info-text p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #555;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #666;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        .rule-list {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
        }
        .rule-list li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #ccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <a href="paid.html" class="back-link">← 返回付费项目</a>
    
    <div class="commission-card">
        <div class="coming-soon-icon">✍️</div>
        <h1>文章约稿</h1>
        <div class="status-badge">⏳ 暂未开放</div>
        
        <div class="info-text">
            <p>📖 约稿服务正在筹备中，敬请期待。</p>
            <p>📝 开放后将提供以下服务：</p>
            <ul class="rule-list">
                <li>✓ 定制故事创作</li>
                <li>✓ 角色设定扩充</li>
                <li>✓ 世界观描述</li>
                <li>✓ 3次免费修改</li>
            </ul>
            <p>📧 如有紧急需求，可先通过邮件咨询：<strong>arseeya@outlook.com</strong></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888;">具体规则以《完整网站使用条款》第5条为准</p>
        </div>
        
        <button class="btn" disabled>暂未开放</button>
    </div>
    
    <footer>© Arseeya. All Rights Reserved | <a href="terms.html" style="color:#aaa;">📜 完整条款</a></footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>